<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 02:15:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普推迟封口费审判的最后努力失败</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-loses-last-ditch-bid-to-delay-hush-money-trial/articleshow/109147936.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109147936.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 请求推迟 4 月 15 日在曼哈顿进行的刑事审判，该审判与一名色情明星的封口费有关，但遭到纽约上诉法官的拒绝。该审判涉及 34 项伪造业务记录罪。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 01:12:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-loses-last-ditch-bid-to-delay-hush-money-trial/articleshow/109147936.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列首次部署C-Dome防御系统</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-deploys-c-dome-defence-system-for-the-first-time/articleshow/109147820.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109147820.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列军方周二表示，以色列首次部署了名为“C-Dome”的舰载防御系统，以应对进入该国南部城市埃拉特附近领空的“可疑”目标。以色列国防军在周二早些时候发布的一份声明中表示：“在埃拉特地区响起敌方飞机渗透的警报后，以色列国防军海军部队发现了一个可疑的空中目标进入以色列领土。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 00:56:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-deploys-c-dome-defence-system-for-the-first-time/articleshow/109147820.cms</guid></item><item><title>月球咬入黄色球体：日全食在北美投下阴影</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/moon-bites-into-yellow-orb-total-solar-eclipse-casts-shadow-over-n-america/articleshow/109146696.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109146696.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周一的日全食吸引了从墨西哥到加拿大的北美观众。数百万人目睹了这一天体事件，经历了白天的黑暗并提醒了地球的宇宙位置。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 23:02:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/moon-bites-into-yellow-orb-total-solar-eclipse-casts-shadow-over-n-america/articleshow/109146696.cms</guid></item><item><title>穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼在沙特会见巴基斯坦总理，敦促印巴谈判解决克什米尔问题</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/mohammed-bin-salman-meets-pak-pm-in-saudi-urges-india-pak-talks-to-resolve-kashmir-issue/articleshow/109146387.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109146387.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;沙特阿拉伯强调伊斯兰堡和新德里之间进行对话，以解决包括克什米尔在内的悬而未决的问题。此前的联合声明和当前的讨论都强调双边解决强生争端有利于地区和平与稳定。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 22:56:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/mohammed-bin-salman-meets-pak-pm-in-saudi-urges-india-pak-talks-to-resolve-kashmir-issue/articleshow/109146387.cms</guid></item><item><title>梵蒂冈将代孕、变性手术、性别流动视为对人类尊严的威胁……</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/vatican-casts-surrogacy-sex-change-surgery-gender-fluidity-as-threat-to-human-dignity-/articleshow/109146135.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109146135.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周一，梵蒂冈认为变性手术、性别流动和代孕是对人类尊严的严重侵犯，将它们与堕胎和安乐死并列为违背上帝对人类计划的活动。梵蒂冈教义办公室发布了“无限尊严”，这是一份长达 20 页的声明，已经酝酿了五年。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 22:51:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/vatican-casts-surrogacy-sex-change-surgery-gender-fluidity-as-threat-to-human-dignity-/articleshow/109146135.cms</guid></item><item><title>加沙休战谈判陷入僵局，比比称拉法进攻日期已定</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/gaza-truce-talks-deadlocked-bibi-says-date-set-for-rafah-offensive/articleshow/109145969.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109145969.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯官方报告称，开罗加沙战争停火谈判没有取得任何进展。内塔尼亚胡计划入侵哈马斯最后的堡垒拉法。拜登反对入侵，因为这可能会对平民造成伤害。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 22:48:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/gaza-truce-talks-deadlocked-bibi-says-date-set-for-rafah-offensive/articleshow/109145969.cms</guid></item><item><title>从“薰衣草”到“爸爸在哪里？”：以色列如何使用人工智能工具打击哈马斯武装分子</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/from-lavender-to-wheres-daddy-how-israel-is-using-ai-tools-to-hit-hamas-militants/articleshow/109133909.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109133909.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列军方在加沙的人工智能行动因造成平民伤亡而受到批评，正面临审查。薰衣草系统的错误识别问题和最少的人为监督引起了人们的担忧。布莱恩娜·罗森批评以色列的目标标准，拜登则警告不要进行不分青红皂白的轰炸。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 10:59:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/from-lavender-to-wheres-daddy-how-israel-is-using-ai-tools-to-hit-hamas-militants/articleshow/109133909.cms</guid></item><item><title>融雪引发俄罗斯乌拉尔地区创纪录洪水</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/record-floods-in-russias-urals-triggered-by-melting-snow/articleshow/109130968.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109130968.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;迅速融化的积雪导致俄罗斯乌拉尔山脉发生严重洪水，欧洲主要河流水位上涨，迫使数千人撤离。欧洲第三长河乌拉尔河水位迅速上涨，冲破奥尔斯克的一座水坝​​，哈萨克斯坦附近的奥伦堡地区宣布进入紧急状态。奥伦堡河流预计将达到危险水位，影响 50 万居民。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:50:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/record-floods-in-russias-urals-triggered-by-melting-snow/articleshow/109130968.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登政府宣布拨款 66 亿美元，确保美国制造领先的微芯片</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-administration-announces-6-6-billion-dollars-to-ensure-leading-edge-microchips-are-built-in-us/articleshow/109129937.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109129937.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;拜登政府承诺向台积电提供 66 亿美元资金，用于扩建亚利桑那州的工厂，提高先进微芯片的国内生产，并加强美国半导体产业。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:29:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-administration-announces-6-6-billion-dollars-to-ensure-leading-edge-microchips-are-built-in-us/articleshow/109129937.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国在国际法院就向以色列供应武器的种族灭绝案进行斗争</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/at-icj-germany-battles-genocide-case-over-arms-supply-to-israel/articleshow/109148198.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109148198.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 01:43:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/at-icj-germany-battles-genocide-case-over-arms-supply-to-israel/articleshow/109148198.cms</guid></item><item><title>国际原子能机构负责人表示，对扎波罗热核电站的袭击大大增加了事故风险</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/attacks-on-zaporizhzhia-nuclear-plant-significantly-increase-accident-risk-iaea-head-says/articleshow/109130350.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109130350.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国原子能监督机构负责人批评无人机袭击乌克兰扎波罗热核电站核反应堆，警告发生核事故的风险增加。拉斐尔·马里亚诺·格罗西证实，反应堆安全壳结构遭受了三起直接袭击。尽管俄罗斯指责乌克兰发动了这次袭击，但联合国机构没有指责乌克兰。基辅当局没有立即对这一事件发表评论。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:29:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/attacks-on-zaporizhzhia-nuclear-plant-significantly-increase-accident-risk-iaea-head-says/articleshow/109130350.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方报告准备广泛动员预备役人员</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-military-reports-readiness-for-broad-mobilization-of-reservists/articleshow/109130238.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109130238.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列国防军宣布了从防御转向进攻的计划，重点是动员预备役人员。北方司令部完成紧急储备准备工作，迅速调动兵力。以色列国防军表示，储存的设备和工具由技术和后勤局（J4）的通信、后勤和医疗人员维护。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:25:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-military-reports-readiness-for-broad-mobilization-of-reservists/articleshow/109130238.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰否认袭击俄罗斯控制的核电站</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-denies-attacking-russian-held-nuclear-plant/articleshow/109130062.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109130062.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰指责俄罗斯散布有关无人机袭击扎波罗热核电站的错误信息。乌克兰虚假信息反制中心主任安德烈·科瓦连科中尉表示，俄罗斯正在不断升级挑衅，并谎称乌克兰军队袭击了该工厂。科瓦连科强调，俄罗斯正在利用无人机制造来自乌克兰对核电站安全构成威胁的虚假叙述。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:20:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-denies-attacking-russian-held-nuclear-plant/articleshow/109130062.cms</guid></item><item><title>X 挑战巴西“强制”封锁某些账户的命令</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/x-challenges-brazils-forced-order-to-block-certain-accounts/articleshow/109130003.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109130003.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:18:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/x-challenges-brazils-forced-order-to-block-certain-accounts/articleshow/109130003.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯外长谢尔盖·拉夫罗夫访问北京强调与最强大政治盟友的关系</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/russia-foreign-minister-sergey-lavrov-visits-beijing-to-emphasize-ties-with-strongest-political-ally/articleshow/109129856.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109129856.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯外交部长谢尔盖·拉夫罗夫抵达北京，在乌克兰冲突中加强与中国的关系。这两个威权大国都致力于扩大其全球影响力，特别是在非洲、中东和南美洲。中国支持俄罗斯的说法，即西方行动引发了普京在2022年的攻击，但没有提供具体证据。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:15:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/russia-foreign-minister-sergey-lavrov-visits-beijing-to-emphasize-ties-with-strongest-political-ally/articleshow/109129856.cms</guid></item><item><title>加沙冲突已过去 6 个多月：有多少以色列人仍被哈马斯扣为人质？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/over-6-months-into-gaza-conflict-how-many-israelis-are-still-being-held-hostage-by-hamas/articleshow/109129390.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109129390.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列在释放哈马斯加沙渗透袭击中劫持的人质方面面临挑战，此次袭击导致 1,163 人死亡，33,000 名巴勒斯坦人死亡。包括 11 名外国人在内的 134 名人质仍处于以色列国防军的猛烈轰炸之中。与哈马斯的谈判要求停火、以色列国防军撤军、释放囚犯以及让加沙人返回释放。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:08:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/over-6-months-into-gaza-conflict-how-many-israelis-are-still-being-held-hostage-by-hamas/articleshow/109129390.cms</guid></item><item><title>北美数百万人等待日全食</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/millions-across-north-america-await-total-solar-eclipse/articleshow/109129304.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109129304.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;北美数百万人等待日全食，因为月亮挡住了太阳超过 4 分钟。日食粉丝沿着全食之路聚集。在北美，在全食路径之外将可以看到日偏食。专家建议使用太阳能眼镜以安全观看，以免眼睛受伤。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:06:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/millions-across-north-america-await-total-solar-eclipse/articleshow/109129304.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国因加沙种族灭绝指控面临联合国最高法庭审判</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-faces-top-un-court-date-over-gaza-genocide-claims/articleshow/109123908.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109123908.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 《种族灭绝公约》，又称《防止及惩治种族灭绝罪公约》，是联合国为应对大屠杀暴行于1948年制定的。该条约的主要目标是确保此类可怕事件不再发生，特别是在 600 万欧洲犹太人遭到种族灭绝之后。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 08:58:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-faces-top-un-court-date-over-gaza-genocide-claims/articleshow/109123908.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗外长称，美国为袭击以色列领事馆“开绿灯”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-gave-israel-green-light-for-consulate-hit-says-iran-foreign-min/articleshow/109148228.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109148228.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 01:46:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-gave-israel-green-light-for-consulate-hit-says-iran-foreign-min/articleshow/109148228.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯称乌克兰袭击了核电站，基辅否认是袭击的幕后黑手</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-says-ukraine-struck-nuclear-plant-kyiv-denies-it-was-behind-the-attack/articleshow/109123436.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109123436.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯表示，乌克兰周日三度袭击了俄罗斯军队控制的扎波罗热核电站，并要求西方做出回应，但基辅表示与袭击无关。国际原子能机构表示，这是自 2022 年 11 月以来欧洲最大核电站首次成为直接攻击目标。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 06:17:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-says-ukraine-struck-nuclear-plant-kyiv-denies-it-was-behind-the-attack/articleshow/109123436.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>